
### Template 3: Documentation Focused

```markdown
# Project Name

Detailed documentation for your project.

## Documentation

Comprehensive documentation can be found at [Docs](https://your-project-docs-url.com).

## Features

- Highlight key features with explanations.

## Getting Started

Guide users through installation, configuration, and initial setup.

## Usage

In-depth usage examples with code snippets and explanations.

## API Reference

If your project has an API, provide detailed documentation here.

## Contributing

Contribution guidelines, code of conduct, and how to set up the development environment.

## Roadmap

Future plans, upcoming features, and improvements.

